A perl hack for burning audio cds out of mp3/ogg/flac/wav files
	
mp3roaster is a perl hack for burning audio cds out of mp3, ogg vorbis, flac
and wav files. the main highlights of this application are an easy to use
command line syntax and automatic volume leveling support for best audio cd
quality.

in order to normalize the audio level of all files which will be burned on cds
mp3roaster requires some free hard disk space.